long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension brings the popular Geometry Dash 2 game right to your Chrome browser with single click.

The extension has the classic Geometry Dash 2 gameplay you know. Jump and dodge through 50 levels filled with spikes and obstacles.

This extension gives you the full Geometry Dash 2 experience with no interruptions or popups.

The Geometry Dash 2 has 5 worlds and 10 levels in each world.

Your goal is to reach the end of each level without hitting obstacles. Famous for its challenging levels, patterns and timing.

Install this rhythm-based platformer game and start jumping in!

Feel free to leave a review or share it with friends if you enjoy it. Your feedback helps us improve and make it even better.
